{"tid":158740,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫貢獻社會？","createTime":"2017-03-16T13:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T00:10:01.000Z","uid":7109,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c985c552630722c767ea576ac1a36cca5dcd89ab","tid":158740,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"成日都話上一代貢獻社會多年云云<br />\n佢地揾食賺錢就叫貢獻社會？<br />\n真係有人抱住呢個心態去返工㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535ae7933b8a16e9f2e985008118caa94c8d3309","tid":158740,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"c745c88bd12095ca42d607bb4eb1978940480eb9","tid":158740,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"炒起曬D野叫貢獻"},{"pid":"292f5512ebdb82b919a2bc8e6a77cd1f7ee3acce","tid":158740,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"每個人都貢獻緊架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704167751051e963ef09ac9a2934f5cfa02b155d","tid":158740,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"仲要用貢獻社會多年嚟做光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6534e29d312b237600992881245d306feba938","tid":158740,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"貢獻國家更難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b46f1874787f23c23cd5156272ac7250ec1bdda","tid":158740,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貢獻國家更難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d64631f005d39083c4208caa6ecc4a4cd6aeb3","tid":158740,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab257c813bb526eb97f1516684c5673d7bbea527","tid":158740,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n進貢廢老同垃圾制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26336bf2f5a63752c93f37c24a9f335446379d2d","tid":158740,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n進貢廢老同垃圾制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676eba87827451dc76522b120ad126c66cdd82b9","tid":158740,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"認真答：<br />\n可以問自己可唔可以稱得上係頂天立地、堂堂正正、盡心盡力嘅人。係嘅，你就可以大聲講自己有貢獻社會。<br />\n至於做唔到嗰啲，又話自己有貢獻社會，係自取其辱。"},{"pid":"ed1661e0fa793199b92ee7839641c0bc3826037c","tid":158740,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答：<br />\n可以問自己可唔可以稱得上係頂天立地、堂堂正正、盡心盡力嘅人。係嘅，你就可以大聲講自己有貢獻社會。<br />\n至於做唔到嗰啲，又話自己有貢獻社會，係自取其辱。</blockquote><br />\n個社會自動將老人家=貢獻社會嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeafa0df6fbf56f3e207acd19c27762358c19afc","tid":158740,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真答：<br />\n可以問自己可唔可以稱得上係頂天立地、堂堂正正、盡心盡力嘅人。係嘅，你就可以大聲講自己有貢獻社會。<br />\n至於做唔到嗰啲，又話自己有貢獻社會，係自取其辱。</blockquote><br />\n個社會自動將老人家=貢獻社會嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打開post都搵到人回應，即係你唔係唯一一個覺得社會出左事嘅人。<br />\n但係要<strong>自己</strong>心裡好過，係觀察自己有無按自己嘅定義同準則貢獻社會。世上有七十億人，我無可能用自己同晒我身邊嘅人比，所以用自己做基準比較自己，係最舒服嘅方法。<br />\n希望巴打生活如意。"},{"pid":"5a6cb6dda799a6c9649166cb1b7d7c18311baa64","tid":158740,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"雖然我不滿用「貢獻社會」作為道德光環甚至乎政治本錢。<br />\n<br />\n但無論係邊一個年代，我都認為好多職業都係為社會做緊貢獻。<br />\n無論地盤工人、裝修師父甚至係餐飲業嘅咁多職員等勞動階層，定還是科研人員、醫生、會計同我呢啲小小嘅IT狗等等。<br />\n(唔敢提警察，戴頭盔)<br />\n<br />\n有人工呢個係必然，但唔可以因為佢地接受咗報酬而否認咗佢地為社會發展帶來嘅貢獻。<br />\n我覺得香港太多人對部分行業嘅人不尊敬。<br />\n<br />\n可能有些人返工只係hea做，或者公司政策太過現實，從來無認真對待過工作，令你會覺得唔值得尊敬此人或是此行業。<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得每一個人都應該有責任去矯正呢啲社會上冷漠嘅表面睇法。<br />\n唔好畀下一代人認為返工只係為咗賺錢、生活養家，自己做過啲咩似乎都係毫無意義，失去咗工作嘅動力。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 不是正義撚<br />\nsorry for off topic..."}]}